headline: Cubby Secures $63 Million in Series A Funding Round Led by Growth Equity at Goldman Sachs Alternatives
summary: NEW YORK, January 22, 2026--Cubby, a property management platform focused on serving the needs of self-storage operators with integrated revenue management, call management, and e-commerce capabilities, today announced it has raised $63 million Series A. This minority investment was led by Growth Equity at Goldman Sachs Alternatives, with participation from existing investors.
